Package: kegg-shiny-app
Title: Evolutionary-informed KEGG Pathway Visualization and Enrichment Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Stefan", "Manolache", , "stefanmanol@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-3326-985X"))
Description: A Shiny web application for interactive visualization and analysis of KEGG pathways.
    Provides tools for gene set enrichment analysis, pathway network visualization,
    and evolutionary analysis using phylostratum data. Integrates with UniProt for
    protein structure information and supports gene validation and mapping.
